The '''''African Human Rights Law Journal''''' publishes [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] contributions dealing with human rights related topics of relevance to [[Africa]], Africans, and scholars of Africa. The journal appears twice a year, in March and October.
== Indexing == The journal is indexed in the [[International Bibliography of the Social Sciences]] (IBBS).
